	<div class="details space-y-8 spacer-b-md">

		<p>These terms and conditions apply to all website maintenance and hosting services provided by Ryan Roberts trading as Yep Digital. Web design and development services are subject to separate terms, details of which are provided at the time of engagement.</p>

		<div class="space-y-4">
			<h2 class="font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading spacer-t-xs">
				Billing & Payment
			</h2>
			<ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-4 md:pl-5 space-y-4">
				<li>Maintenance and hosting is billed annually, in advance, upon launch of the project. Subsequent invoices are raised on or around the same date each year.</li>
				<li>Payment is by bank transfer, payable within 14 days of invoice date. All necessary account details will be included on each invoice.</li>
				<li>I am not currently VAT registered; no VAT will be charged unless my VAT status changes, in which case you will be notified.</li>
				<li>Invoices not settled within 14 days are subject to statutory interest at 8% above the UK base rate, in accordance with the Late Payment of Commercial Debts Act 1998.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-4">
			<h2 class="font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading spacer-t-xs">
				Pricing
			</h2>

			<ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-4 md:pl-5 space-y-4">
				<li>The annual fee is outlined in your original project proposal, estimate, or invoice.</li>
				<li>Pricing is subject to change. I will provide a minimum of 30 days written notice before any price increase takes effect. Continued use of the service following notice of a price change constitutes acceptance of the new rate.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-4">
			<h2 class="font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading spacer-t-xs">
				What's Included
			</h2>

			<p>The annual fee covers the following services, as described in full on the <a href="{{ '/info/hosting/' | url }}">hosting</a> and <a href="{{ '/info/hosting/' | url }}">maintenance</a> information pages. CMS websites require an active maintenance plan; static websites may be hosted without one.</p>

			<ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-4 md:pl-5 space-y-4">
				<li>Regular CMS and server updates, with critical updates applied immediately.</li>
				<li>Security and server management, including SSL certificate renewal and security patches.</li>
				<li>Minute-by-minute uptime monitoring and proactive issue investigation.</li>
				<li>Daily backups stored in multiple secure locations.</li>
				<li>Minor content updates and technical support, with responses typically within one business day.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-4">
			<h2 class="font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading spacer-t-xs">
				Cancellation
			</h2>

			<ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-4 md:pl-5 space-y-4">
				<li>You may cancel your maintenance and hosting plan at any time by getting in touch at <a href="mailto:ryan@yep.digital">ryan@yep.digital</a>.</li>
				<li>If you do not wish to renew at the end of the annual period, please notify me at least 14 days before the renewal date. No refund is due in this case as the service will continue until the end of the paid period.</li>
				<li>If you cancel and migrate your website to another provider, hosting will remain active until your domain is pointed away from my servers. A refund for the unused portion of the annual fee will be calculated from that point, minus a £30 administration charge. Any assistance required with the migration is available at my standard hourly rate.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-4">
			<h2 class="font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading spacer-t-xs">
				Non-Payment & Suspension
			</h2>
			<ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-4 md:pl-5 space-y-4">
				<li>If an invoice remains unpaid 14 days after the due date, I will attempt to make contact to resolve the matter.</li>
				<li>If payment has not been received within 30 days of the due date, a formal reminder will be issued advising that suspension of service is pending.</li>
				<li>If no payment or response is received within a further 30 days, the website will be suspended and an email notification sent.</li>
				<li>Websites that remain suspended for 30 days without payment or contact will be archived. Restoration after archiving may not be possible.</li>
				<li>I understand that circumstances vary and aim to be flexible wherever possible. If you are experiencing difficulties, please get in touch as early as possible so we can find a reasonable way forward.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-4">
			<h2 class="font-bold tracking-[-0.0125em] text-white text-heading spacer-t-xs">
				Governing Law
			</h2>
			<p>These terms are governed by the laws of Scotland. Any disputes arising from services provided under these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the Scottish courts.</p>
		</div>

		<p>If you have any questions, feel free to get in touch at <a href="mailto:ryan@yep.digital">ryan@yep.digital</a>.</p>

